text: good grows with her in her days every
man shall eat in safety under his own
vine but he plants and seeing the merry
songs of peace to all his neighbors God
shall be truly known and those about her
from her shall read the perfect ways of
honor and by those claim their greatness
not by blood she shall be to the
happiness of England an aged princess
many days shall see her and yet no day
without a deed to crown it
